snippet.textDisplay: Stephen, please keep rolling. The show must go on. My 2.5 year old loves you and can't get enough of your theme song. He'll even chant "Colbert" to make me put it on. Plus a lot of us here in the quarantined European media do our duty to keep the public informed despite all the dangers and lacking safety measures. We've grown used to your regular updates and digests of US news, as crazy as that sounds. You are a lifesaver in these difficult times (virus not included). Even without an audience, you are the best. If you ever come to Prague, stop by the local NPR - Czech Radio and look me up. I am no Jacinda Ardern (the beard's too long), but I got a castle. :-D. As one of our legendary quotes says: "We are with you, stay with us..."
